      "id": "infrastructure--5011409d-b736-48af-b734-0adbbecfa70d",
      "name": "Compromised Proxy and Staging Servers",
      "description": "Compromised legitimate servers used by Sandworm for proxying traffic, exfiltrating data, and reconnaissance. These IPs were observed accessing router management interfaces and attempting authentication to online services.",
